data.description:
Come see this IMMACULATE three bedroom, two and a half bath townhome located in the desirable neighborhood of Canterbury Place of Abacoa. Top features of this townhome include keyless entry, high ceilings, IMPACT windows and doors, hardwood flooring, newer carpet, plantation shutters, fresh paint and a home generator hookup.The kitchen offers a breakfast nook, pantry, granite countertops, wood cabinets and upgraded stainless steel appliances. Off of the kitchen is a private courtyard leading to the detached two car garage. The laundry is located on the second floor, along with three spacious bedrooms and two bathrooms. Included in your HOA fee is a beautiful clubhouse with fitness center and pool. There's also an abundance of green space throughout the subdivision for you to enjoy. Jupiter schools are A-Rated! A short distance away is Lighthouse Elementary School and Jupiter Middle School. Canterbury Place is also zoned for Jupiter High School. In addition, you can enjoy the local findings Jupiter has to offer such as downtown Abacoa, Jupiter Amphitheater, Roger Dean Stadium, shops, restaurants and the Florida beaches!
Don't miss this one!
